name: LivingJumpEvent
description: LivingJumpEvent is fired when an Entity jumps. This event is fired whenever an Entity jumps in EntityLivingBase#jump(), EntityMagmaCube#jump(), and EntityHorse#jump(). This event is fired via the ForgeHooks#onLivingJump(EntityLivingBase) . This event is not Cancelable . This event does not have a result. HasResult This event is fired on the MinecraftForge#EVENT_BUS .
